UPDATE products SET 
  descriptionEn = 'A flexible abrasion resistant polyurethane elastomer for the repair, rebuilding and coating of rubber components and metal surfaces. Belzona 2111 (D&A Hi-Build Elastomer) combines flexibility with exceptional abrasion resistance, making it ideal for protecting rubber and elastomeric components. It provides superior adhesion to both rubber and metal substrates and maintains flexibility after cure. The material resists degradation from ozone, UV exposure, and chemical attack. It can be applied to create protective coatings or to rebuild worn rubber components. Typical applications include conveyor belt repairs, pump seal protection, hose coupling restoration, and rubber component rebuilding.',
